撞鬼 痴線上加痴線 咁咪死...</span><br />\n<br />\n自己跳樓死唔緊要<br />\n唔好禍及家人朋友</blockquote><br />\n如果紅字，一半係。<br />\n另一半就係你本身係唔係一個好人，我自己會形容為左膠。<br />\n如果你左膠果半都唔係，但你又有紅字，都係算吧啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔知自己點先算係好人<br />\n<br />\n你有學? 係咪可以介紹?"},{"pid":"088c68e00c43d25f6f14b79458dcf746f52de011","tid":137171,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解想學？</blockquote><br />\n生活困頓多年<br />\n人生新方向<br />\n學黎睇下有冇轉變<br />\n可以自保<br />\n學多d可以幫到人</blockquote><br />\n咁唔一定學六壬都得既<br />\n同埋亂幫人自己都麻煩"},{"pid":"dfae96ff61d84fbb69b31b4705a659f68278c08c","tid":137171,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外人入黎八卦<br />\n爸爸好似有過教但冇認真學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157dc7bb96bdc1ea8f279d377799ccaa4767bc9b","tid":137171,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外人入黎八卦<br />\n爸爸好似有過教但冇認真學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想學"},{"pid":"d57dd7aad8e4d117f89e822d5d8380bf42e79ffd","tid":137171,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:28:20.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"e0d56275809cb3c97c4643b139fc4a81864dd6db","tid":137171,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外人入黎八卦<br />\n爸爸好似有過教但冇認真學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想學</blockquote><br />\n點解會選擇六一一"},{"pid":"0c3fe4cd1e6dc5dd91febe7ce1e137585fb7d2e3","tid":137171,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src